      "description": "You've probably heard of the \"10,000 Hours\" theory, and you might have been intimidated by the daunting prospect of it. But the truth is, all you need to do is start. The first second you begin holds significance.\n\nI developed the \"10000 Hours\" timer app with the hope of bringing a little bit of light to the chaotic, out-of-control, and seemingly meaningless situations. Create your life project and nurture it every day with time. Enjoy the peace and satisfaction of every second slipping through your fingers. Will it bloom and bear fruit? Most likely, it will. And if it doesn't? Enjoy the mindful process, explore, and understand yourself a bit more; that in itself is a blessing.\n\nWhat can you do with \"10000 Hours\"?\n\n1. Create and time your life projects daily: It could be a subject for students, a hobby for workers, a small thing you want to try, or a tiny habit you want to develop. Believe in the power of time, change starts at every moment.\n\n2. View project data and charts: Review your project check-in habits and time investment.\n\n3. Manage all projects: Archive completed projects and reopen projects that need continuation.\n\n4. iCloud automatic synchronization of project data: Easily continue even if you reinstall the app or change devices.\n\nIf you have any comments or suggestions during the use of the product, please feel free to email us. We are always delighted with your feedback! \nmailto:zjy0314@icloud.com\n\n----------------------\n\nWe do not collect any of your personal privacy. For the privacy policy, visit: https://zjymm0314.notion.site/d98112944f644ca18554b560bb0bf5f7?pvs=4",
